<template>
  <v-container fluid class="down-top-padding">
    <BaseBreadcrumb :title="page.title" :icon="page.icon" :breadcrumbs="breadcrumbs"></BaseBreadcrumb>
    <v-row>
      <v-col cols="12" sm="12">
        <BaseCard heading="Time Pickers - Colors">
          <TimePickerColors></TimePickerColors>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Time Pickers - Disabled">
          <TimePickerDisabled></TimePickerDisabled>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Time Pickers - Read-only">
          <TimePickerReadonly></TimePickerReadonly>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Time Pickers - 24h format">
          <TimePicker24hFormat></TimePicker24hFormat>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Time Pickers - Allowed times">
          <TimePickerAllowedTimes></TimePickerAllowedTimes>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Time Pickers - Setting picker width">
          <TimePickerSettingPickerWidth></TimePickerSettingPickerWidth>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Time Pickers - AM/PM switch in title">
          <TimePickerAmPmSwitchinTitle></TimePickerAmPmSwitchinTitle>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Time Pickers - No title">
          <TimePickerNoTitle></TimePickerNoTitle>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Time Pickers - With seconds">
          <TimePickerWithSeconds></TimePickerWithSeconds>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Time Pickers - Scrollable">
          <TimePickerScrollable></TimePickerScrollable>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Time Pickers - In dialog and menu">
          <TimePickerInDialogMenu></TimePickerInDialogMenu>
        </BaseCard>

        <BaseCard heading="Time Pickers - Range">
          <TimePickerInRange></TimePickerInRange>
        </BaseCard>
      </v-col>
    </v-row>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "TimePickers",

  data: () => ({
    page: {
      title: "TimePickers"
    },
    breadcrumbs: [
      {
        text: "UI Components",
        disabled: false,
        to: "#"
      },
      {
        text: "TimePickers",
        disabled: true
      }
    ]
  }),
  components: {
    TimePickerColors: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/time-pickers/TimePickerColors"),
    TimePickerDisabled: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/time-pickers/TimePickerDisabled"),
    TimePickerReadonly: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/time-pickers/TimePickerReadonly"),
    TimePicker24hFormat: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/time-pickers/TimePicker24hFormat"),
    TimePickerAllowedTimes: () =>
      import(
        "@/components/vuetifyComponents/time-pickers/TimePickerAllowedTimes"
      ),
    TimePickerSettingPickerWidth: () =>
      import(
        "@/components/vuetifyComponents/time-pickers/TimePickerSettingPickerWidth"
      ),
    TimePickerAmPmSwitchinTitle: () =>
      import(
        "@/components/vuetifyComponents/time-pickers/TimePickerAmPmSwitchinTitle"
      ),
    TimePickerNoTitle: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/time-pickers/TimePickerNoTitle"),
    TimePickerWithSeconds: () =>
      import(
        "@/components/vuetifyComponents/time-pickers/TimePickerWithSeconds"
      ),
    TimePickerScrollable: () =>
      import(
        "@/components/vuetifyComponents/time-pickers/TimePickerScrollable"
      ),
    TimePickerInDialogMenu: () =>
      import(
        "@/components/vuetifyComponents/time-pickers/TimePickerInDialogMenu"
      ),
    TimePickerInRange: () =>
      import("@/components/vuetifyComponents/time-pickers/TimePickerInRange")
  }
};
</script>
